{"tid":2324984,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"開庭被爆砸錢開小姐？勝利認了「快樂一下」不是性交易關係","createTime":"2020-12-14T10:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T14:02:30.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f481c2bbdf7f20a435bdc37ace5ad00abd0eec77","tid":2324984,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:42:15.000Z","msg":"南韓天團BIGBANG前成員勝利，因為優異的音樂才華，加上俊秀的外表，廣受許多網友喜愛。然而去年爆出性招待、勾結警方等罪名，爆出「老司機群組」、「勝利事件」，甚至傳性招待日本客戶前，為了「確認女性水準」，會提前帶回家「試車」受到一連串醜聞重擊，良好形象一夕之間全面瓦解，近日受審時更是再爆出，勝利在家中花錢「開小姐」性交易引發熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/01/15/2360833-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F01%2F15%2F2360833-PH.jpg&h=068ee620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲勝利爆一連串醜聞還被證人指家中花錢「開小姐」。（圖／翻攝自勝利IG）<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒報導，勝利涉性交易等8項罪名，日前出席軍事審判時，有名女子出庭作證表示，她在2015年時受邀到達指定地點後，才發現這是勝利首爾麻浦區的住家，兩人不僅曾發生過關係，甚至還從中收益，然而勝利該方的律師否認這項指控，他表示勝利是在不知情是性交易情況下，與該名女子發生性關係。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/04/02/1856536-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F04%2F02%2F1856536-PH.jpg&h=cf0cd266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲勝利承認發生性關係但否認有交易。（圖／翻攝自勝利IG）<br />\n<br />\n原本一連串「勝利事件」影響，勝利延期一次入伍當兵，後來順利今年3月入伍，但剛好撞上武漢肺炎（COVID-19、新冠肺炎）肆虐關係不開放現場，未開放粉絲送別，他的案件則送往軍事法庭繼續審理，不過也因為軍事法庭判刑更重的關係，不少粉絲都相當替他擔心，先前還在推特上發起「勝利是無辜的」等活動。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，因為勝利事件延伸出「鄭俊英群組事件」，目前已有多人定罪，其中包括歌手鄭俊英遭判刑5年、歌手崔鍾訓遭判刑2年6個月，影響範圍相當廣泛，也讓大票粉絲跟著心碎。目前對於所有指控，勝利僅認8項罪名中違反《外匯交易法》一項，此案將於12月29日進行下次聆訊。"},{"pid":"a0a8ef7d78dbaa16e13ed1980c9b0e35dfaf4aa3","tid":2324984,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:43:34.000Z","msg":"bigbang回歸未<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267c5b24deff7e78849b00560b96185222418df5","tid":2324984,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0a8ef7d78dbaa16e13ed1980c9b0e35dfaf4aa3","tid":2324984,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:43:34.000Z","msg":"bigbang回歸未<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:45:11.000Z","msg":"2021(好似)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759a9e3dd5fc2a1a1fe16c1169b5f808afb3a8aa","tid":2324984,"uid":339805,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:46:58.000Z","msg":"勝利（已失敗）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0f4722ffa326d8d9f2e3667c6a50e43e2b4f85","tid":2324984,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"759a9e3dd5fc2a1a1fe16c1169b5f808afb3a8aa","tid":2324984,"uid":339805,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:46:58.000Z","msg":"勝利（已失敗）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:52:12.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aad70cd47d5b26fdd73124da3c239cbd35ac9ac","tid":2324984,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ea0f4722ffa326d8d9f2e3667c6a50e43e2b4f85","tid":2324984,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"759a9e3dd5fc2a1a1fe16c1169b5f808afb3a8aa","tid":2324984,"uid":339805,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:46:58.000Z","msg":"勝利（已失敗）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T10:52:12.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-14T11:14:44.000Z","msg":"你幾時喺個名到加（已綠帽）？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4ab3512f5786c2c5f2fe853d74bde48099e274","tid":2324984,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5aad70cd47d5b26fdd73124da3c239cbd35ac9ac","tid":2324984,"uid":136770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ea0f4722ffa326d8d9f2e3667c6